headline: PNC Launches Monthly Consumer Health Check to Deliver Real-Time Pulse on U.S. Spending and the Economy
summary: The PNC Financial Services Group, Inc. (NYSE: PNC) today announced the launch of the PNC Monthly Consumer Health Check, a new series of concise, data‑driven updates that leverages PNC's proprietary, anonymized and aggregated data to provide a real‑time view of consumer activity and the broader U.S. economy. The new report, available now, will publish monthly, offering timely insights to business leaders, investors and households navigating an evolving economic landscape.
